<plot>Documentary about one of the most famous masters of Capoeira (an Afro-Brazilian martial art and dance), Vicente Ferreira Pastinha, aka Mestre Pastinha, guardian of the traditional style of Capoeira, the Angola style. He was responsible for the renewal of this fight through the revival of its deepest roots and origins, and played it for more than 80 years.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?425651</url></doc>
